Package: novelCoViD
Type: Package
Title: live worldwide data from CoViD-19
Version: 0.1.0
Author: c(person("Rasa", "Ashrafi", email = "rasa.ashrafi@gmail.com", role = c("cre","aut")))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <yourself@somewhere.net>
Description: this package allows users to obtain live worldwide data from the novel CoronaVirus Disease, CoViD-19 as published by the Johns Hopkins University data repository on Github, as well as, provide basic map and plot functions to investigate these datasets.
